  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754120/extras/0affb0dfa96fb2af809a7874be926667.avif?t=1738797822\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Ninja Stealth III is a casual game with 30 challenging levels where your only goal is to get the computer inside the room, can you do it?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 30 new challenging levels<br></li><li> New achievements<br></li><li> Move inside the room without being detected<br></li><li> Hide yourself behind the boxes<br></li><li> Camouflage yourself as a box<br></li><li> Have fun!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Warning:</h2>If you want an easy game or you can't deal with frustration, DO NOT buy this game!",
